Depends: slop, maim, imagemagick, tesseract-ocr, tesseract-ocr-eng, tesseract-ocr-rus, translate-shell, yad, xdotool, xclip, x11-utils, libnotify-bin
Description: Overlay OCR Translator for Linux
 Recognizes text from a selected screen area, translates it and shows a semi-transparent overlay near the selection.
